Summary: An Aircraft in the sky that would dissolve and reappear in a different part of the skr.
divs: Sighting Details1: Helendale CA 2: Streak in the sky 3: Fighter Aircraft 4: Moved through the sky with contrails and then would dissolve, then would reappear higher in the sky and would then dissolve again. 5: Being familiar with all matter of aircraft it was unusual. 6: it Dissolved and was lost.
trends: There has been one other sighting in Helendale
There were no other sightings in Helendale on or around June 16th 2012
